metadata.description:
SPOTLIGHT WK 1

The first in our SPOTLIGHT series is the winner of our FREE .03 remix competition.

The original beat was produced by the incredibly talented LNRZ community member Lucas Radouch. The track was graced with some sweet vocals from LNRZ newcomer Ryan King during the remix competition.

We're stoked on how it all came together.

Join LNRZ HQ here: https://guild.xyz/lnrz-hq
